(90, '自由的云彩', 'ziyoudeyuncai@126.com', 'e888f9439a61be1f0a391a44d36d0aea', '刘沛', '2', 'A', '', '15937179290', '514969802', '', '2011-12-14 14:48:46', '2,8,10,15', NULL, NULL, 'C', 'B', 'B', 'C', 'trademake fee', '1,2', 3, 4, '5', 3, 2, '        TRADEMARKS\r\n\r\n1) Fees for trademark searches in Russia.\r\n\r\nDifferent terms and types of trademark searches are available.\r\n\r\n \r\nSearch for	Term	Fee of the Russian PTO (RUR)\r\n		In one class	Each additional class\r\nWord mark	1 month	3000 (~ USD 100)	600 (~ USD 20)\r\n - / -	2 weeks	6000 (~ 200)	1200 (~ 40)\r\n - / -	7-9 days	9000 (~ 300)	1800 (~ 60)\r\n - / -	3 days	18000 (~ 600)	3600 (~ 120)\r\n -/-	1 day	36000 (~1200)	7200 (~240)\r\nGraphical mark	1 month	7500 (~ 250)	1500 (~ 50)\r\n- / -	2 weeks	15000 (~ 500)	3000 (~ 100)\r\n- / -	7-9 days	22500 (~ 750)	4500 (~ 150)\r\n\r\nIf terms of the search are not indicated in the order letter, the one-week search is ordered. In case the Russian transliteration of the mark in Latin is required, the official fees will be raised by 10%.\r\n\r\nOur agent’s fee for ordering the search is USD 200 per trademark independently of a number of classes. Our fees for commenting and advising on search results are USD 250 - USD 320 per hour. In case of urgent search (1 - 3-days search) our service fees will increase by 50%.\r\n\r\n2) Documents and fees for registration of a trademark in Russia (there is no difference between word, color, device and/or combined marks). A multi-class trademark application is allowable:\r\n\r\n1.	Applicant&#039s name and address; \r\n2.	List of goods and/or services (in accordance with the Nice Classification of Goods and Services) for which a trademark should be registered. It should be noted that a class heading does not automatically protect all the goods included in the class. In this light for the broadest protection of your client’s mark it is recommendable to file the class heading and a detailed list of goods your client is interested in most of all (if any);\r\n3.	6 typographic prints of the device/combined mark (8 x 8 cm. or 8 x 10 cm. in size). Prints of a device/combined mark can also be prepared at our end for USD 50;\r\n4.	Power of Attorney (It should be issued by the applicant and signed by the authorized person with indication of his name and position in the company. The date and place of the signature should be indicated as well. Neither notarization nor legalization is required). Please note that the Power of Attorney can be submitted after filing the application. There is no strict term for filing Power of Attorney with the Russian PTO.\r\n5.	In case of claiming conventional priority we need a certified copy of the first (home) application. The filing particulars should correspond to the ones into the first (home) application. It (the first (home) application) can be submitted after filing the application, but within three months from the date of filing a conventional trademark application with the Russian PTO. This term cannot be extended. In should be also noted that a split (partial) priority does not foreseen in Russia.\r\n\r\n	Official fee	Agent’s fee\r\n	Rubles	equivalent in USD	USD\r\nFiling application in one class including examination	10500	~ 375	400\r\n- For each additional class	1500	~ 55	\r\nPatent Office Service Fee	 	5	\r\nLate filing application materials (Power of Attorney, Priority document)	 	 	50\r\nClaiming convention priority in Russia	 	 	100\r\nForwarding Official Filing Receipt	 	 	100\r\n\r\n\r\nIf all required documents are submitted, the cost of filing an application in one class (including the cost for forwarding Official Filing Receipt) is about USD 885. For each additional class the cost increases by USD 50.\r\n\r\nWe would like to draw your attention to the fact that we do not charge our fee for an extra class in an application.\r\n\r\nIn case of an Official Action of Registration (on condition that no objections are raised during the examination) the cost of further prosecution irrespective of the number of classes is about USD 805 (including the Official fee for registration in the amount of 12000 Rubles which is about USD 400 and a Patent Office Service fee in the amount of USD 5). No additional fee for publication is charged. Please note that the above mentioned sum does not include our fee for reviewing of the Official Action of Registration which is USD 250-320 per hour.\r\n\r\nIn case of large list of goods and/or services additional fee for verifying and/or translation of list of goods/services will be charged (USD 20 for 100 words).\r\n\r\nIf a trademark meets the examiner&#039s objections, the cost depends on the services rendered in connection with the objections raised (reporting, advising, overcoming, etc.). \r\n\r\nPlease note that all the Official fees are fixed. But their US dollar’s equivalent depends on the current exchange rate.\r\n\r\nIn view of the above the approximate expenses for one trademark (from filing to registration) in one class will be in the amount of USD 1690 + USD 250-320 per hour for reviewing of the Official Action of Registration (if no objections are raised during its examination). For each additional class the cost increases by USD 50.\r\n\r\nAll the above costs are given without postage expenses, which are about USD 10-20 for forwarding each document. The cost for forwarding Certificate of Registration via DHL is USD 50-60.\r\n\r\nApproximate time frames for the trademark prosecution in Russia:\r\n\r\n(i)	  The Official Filing Receipt is issued within 1-2 months from the date of filing an application; \r\n(ii)	The Official Action is issued within 12-14 months from the date of filing the application.\r\n(iii)	In case of the positive decision the Registration Certificate is issued within 2 months from the date of payment of the Official Fee for registration.\r\n', '       商标\r\n1)俄罗斯境内商标查询费用。\r\n\r\n可提不同期限和类型的商标查询\r\n调查内容	期限	俄罗斯专利和商标局费用（俄罗斯卢布）\r\n		一个类别	每增加一个类别\r\n字标	1月	   3000 (~ USD 